data.description: Massive Canal Front home on an expansive double lot in desirable Eden Pines! Enjoy 120' of water front and a short canal ride out to Open Water! Made for entertaining, this property boasts a spacious great room which flows out to a new screened-in porch, with peaceful Views of the Canal and backyard below. Grill your fresh catch and dine al fresco on the open back deck. The well-appointed kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, abundant storage, and large pantry. Plenty of room for all in this 3 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home, with potential for a 4th bedroom on the main floor. A second-floor laundry closet offers added convenience, and the spacious primary bedroom is equipped with a large walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with soaking tub. Ample room for parking and trailer storage, and just minutes to the Eden Pines boat ramp, stores and restaurants in town! Schedule a tour of this exceptional property today!
